    "en": {
      "title": "A midnight robbery on Semmani Road",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna.Kalviangadu - A gang entered a house on New Semmani Road in the middle of the night and stole petrol from a motorcycle. They also stole a two-wheeler and fled.",
        "While the said incident took place last night, today morning when the people of the house searched for the missing two-wheeler, it was revealed that the motorcycle had also been stolen from the motorcycle. (R)"
      ],
